//	DisconnectAfterDeath: Disconnects character after death in Offline Levelling mode, 0/1
//	ReBuffInterval: Interval of using buff, seconds
//	HealInterval: Interval to use heal buff, seconds
//	HealHPBelow: Percentage value of HP to use heal buff, 0.1 to 1.0, where 1.0 represents 100%
//	DisableMovement: Allows to disable automated character movement, 0/1
//	DisableInfoAbovePlayer: Allows to disable information cloud above player in offline levelling mode, 0/1
